node.text:
@misslhommedieu offering this $15,750,000 Bel Air mansion (@1518belair) with over 9,300 sq ft including 6 bedrooms and 10 bathroms - A true timeless masterpiece featuring the latest in technology, materials and infused with Old World class and spectacular magic. Completely remodeled and completed in 2014. A state-of-the-art open floor plan, grand open kitchen/family room and breakfast nook seating for 10. A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair

node.text:
@ZacMostame offering this $20,995,000 Beverly Hills mansion. Settled above the city lights, this elegant tennis court estate features approximately 16,000 square feet of luxury living, all within the coveted 24-hour guard-gated community, Mulholland Estates. Featuring 7 bedrooms, 10 full bathrooms, a formal entry, dining room, expansive sous-chef style kitchen, and overSized living and entertaining areas which are rich and full of volume. As you walk through the home, you are greeted with floor-to-ceiling doors and windows that lead out to the resort-style backyard with an infinity-edged pool, tennis court, and outdoor dining areas that offer an unparalleled lifestyle of seclusion, luxurious comfort, and lavish entertaining. Additional features include a library/office, elevator, gym, 10-car garage, and an entertainment floor encompassing a home theater, game room, and wine area. The classic yet sophisticated home awaits the next buyer to fully experience the Southern California lifestyle at its best.

Contact @ZacMostame for more information
